            {% render 'pf-eef4a42d' %}
            {% endif %}</div><section data-section-id="pf-b1c3" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-124_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-125_">Stability Factors
</h2></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-140a" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-127_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-128_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-6334eb14-0ad1-4066-be74-224ccddf7cb2"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">One of the notable advantages of the barbell bench press is its stability factor. The barbell allows both arms to work together, distributing the load evenly across the body. This symmetry minimizes muscular imbalances and enhances overall stability during the lift.<br><br>Additionally, using a barbell engages <a href="https://www.ativafit.com/blogs/exercise-tips/best-shoulder-workouts-with-dumbbells?srsltid=AfmBOopL1j4SaVYPZdSw-0joaznEUld4CRGOowYwcz_Myw_UUcf0bpRU" target="_self"><span style="color: rgb(245, 166, 35);">stabilizer muscles throughout the shoulders</span></a><a href="https://www.ativafit.com/blogs/exercise-tips/best-shoulder-workouts-with-dumbbells?srsltid=AfmBOopL1j4SaVYPZdSw-0joaznEUld4CRGOowYwcz_Myw_UUcf0bpRU" target="_self"></a> and <a href="https://www.ativafit.com/blogs/home-gym/get-your-core-fit-with-ativafit-half-ball-balance-trainer?srsltid=AfmBOopPQb1cKDXBNpa1jTX9dqKEEoxC5BST_pPd1bLc88Ennc-N_nWv" target="_self"><span style="color: rgb(245, 166, 35);">core</span></a>, improving joint stability and functional strength. Proper setup and grip width are essential for maximizing this stability and ensuring safety during heavy lifts.</span></p></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-130a" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-131_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-132_">Targets Pecs Directly
</h2></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-965f" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-134_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-135_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-c801be54-c919-4c68-b39e-bb9f92bbdba4"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">The bench press primarily targets the pectoralis major, along with secondary involvement from the triceps and deltoids. The barbell's fixed path ensures that all effort is concentrated on these muscle groups, making it an efficient exercise for building <a href="https://www.ativafit.com/blogs/exercise-tips/enhance-your-upper-body-workout-this-nhl-season?_pos=1&amp;_sid=ab2b06a65&amp;_ss=r" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(245, 166, 35);">upper-body mass.</span></a></span></p></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-548e" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-138_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><img alt="3_2d7984a4-2a5e-411a-a685-6119d7280cba_480x480.webp__PID:9bf8a523-9887-4365-9099-68a1dbe93468" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/3_480x480_2de79bf8-c9ef-4e53-ba51-2a065acb864d.webp?v=1772497448&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/3_480x480_2de79bf8-c9ef-4e53-ba51-2a065acb864d.webp?v=1772497448&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/3_480x480_2de79bf8-c9ef-4e53-ba51-2a065acb864d.webp?v=1772497448&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/3_480x480_2de79bf8-c9ef-4e53-ba51-2a065acb864d.webp?v=1772497448&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/3_480x480_2de79bf8-c9ef-4e53-ba51-2a065acb864d.webp?v=1772497448&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/3_480x480_2de79bf8-c9ef-4e53-ba51-2a065acb864d.webp?v=1772497448&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/3_480x480_2de79bf8-c9ef-4e53-ba51-2a065acb864d.webp?v=1772497448&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/3_480x480_2de79bf8-c9ef-4e53-ba51-2a065acb864d.webp?v=1772497448&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/3_480x480_2de79bf8-c9ef-4e53-ba51-2a065acb864d.webp?v=1772497448&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/3_480x480_2de79bf8-c9ef-4e53-ba51-2a065acb864d.webp?v=1772497448&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/3_480x480_2de79bf8-c9ef-4e53-ba51-2a065acb864d.webp?v=1772497448&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1.5" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image5" class="sc-fscnvs dncZrx pf-139_" store="[object Object]"/></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-14a7" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-140_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-141_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-eed7ab14-a7fa-4fd2-9765-5ee73be2fcf0"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Variations in grip width can further emphasize different parts of the chest; for instance, a narrower grip increases triceps activation, while a wider grip focuses more on the outer pectorals.</span></p></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-5733" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-144_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-145_">Improved Bone Health
</h2></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-e385" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-147_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-148_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-459f67e3-8508-4460-b188-f986228d0d18"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">In addition to muscular benefits, the bench press promotes bone health, according to <a href="https://siriushealth.com.au/bench-press-benefits/" target="_self"><span style="color: rgb(245, 166, 35);">Sirius Health</span></a>. Engaging in resistance training, such as bench pressing, can improve bone density, which is particularly beneficial for preventing osteoporosis.<br><br>Studies have shown that regular weight-bearing exercises can lead to significant enhancements in bone mineral density among individuals of various ages.</span></p></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-d86f" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-151_ pf-container-1 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-152_"><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-153_"><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-154_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-155_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-44278f1e-357d-4b67-8575-40b429a425c2"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content "><strong>Ativafit&nbsp;Lava&nbsp;66&nbsp;Lb Adjustable&nbsp;Dumbbells</strong></span></p><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-158_"><img alt="stars.png__PID:a3e8d3d9-1937-48d1-815e-ed960d0230b8" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/stars.png?v=1762991825&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/stars.png?v=1762991825&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/stars.png?v=1762991825&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2623/4904/files/stars.png?v=176299182